(1, 'Rice', 'long-gain-Basmati-Rice.jpg', 'rice', NULL, '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Basmati Rice</strong> is very much needed resulting from its long grain size and excellent aroma. We are one of the many prominent Manufacturers, Exporters and Suppliers of Basmati Rice from Dhaka, Bangladesh. We make available different varieties of Basmati Rice like <strong>Brown Basmati Rice</strong>,White Basmati Rice and Golden Basmati Rice.Others aromatic Tasy rice is Chini Gura Rice,Kala Jeera Rice The Basmati Rice most of us offer is processed under hygienic conditions. To retain the effective and longer storage of our own Basmati Rice, we pack it in moisture-proof packaging material.</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><br> <strong>For more details please click on the links given below</strong></p>', ''),
