(5, 'Sesame Seeds', 'White-Sesame-Seeds8.jpg', 'sesame-seeds', NULL, '', '<p>The company is a reliable manufacturer, exporter and supplier of <strong>Sesame Seeds</strong> from Dhaka, Bangladesh. We offer the premium quality Sesame Seeds throughout the world. Sesame Seeds are full of copper, magnesium and calcium and therefore are often used in food dressings, pharmaceuticals and insecticides. We distribute bulk quantities of Sesame Seeds at inexpensive rates. Moreover, we ensure zero defects of your ordered products until the final shipment of the lot.</p>', ''),
