(9, 'indenting - Solvents Chemicals', 'TextileChemicals.jpg', 'indenting-solvents-chemicals', NULL, '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">We happen to be engaged in trading associated with a wide range of <strong>Solvents Chemicals&nbsp;</strong>Importer and agent in Bangladesh. Our range comprises <em>Xylene</em>, Toluene, Acetone, Methanol, White Spirit, Butyl Glycol, Ethyl Acetate, Butyl Acetate, Cyclohexanone, etc. Quality is our hallmark and then we follow stringent measures while offering our range. We guarantee that the complete series of products is correctly packed before being handed to the client. We offer our range at industry leading prices.</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>For more details, please click on the links given below</strong></p>', ''),
(10, 'Indenting - Paper Raw Materials', 'Kraft Top Liner Paper.jpg', 'indenting-paper-raw-materials', NULL, '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Our rich vendor base helps us in offering qualitative number <strong>Paper Raw Materials</strong> Importer and agent in Bangladesh that is actually best for various applications. The Paper Raw Materials which can include 100% Virgin Kraft Liner Paper, Kraft Liner Paper, Kraft Top Liner Paper, Test Liner Paper, Virgin White Top Kraft Liner Paper, White Top Liner Paper, Corrugated medium paper, Sack Kraft, Duplex board, Art card, Newsprint, Pulp, West paper, Glue Starch Powder, Corrugel, etc. The Paper known because of its cost effectiveness and optimum quality. Our site delivers our range at industry leading prices.</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><br> <strong>For more details, please click on the links given below</strong></p>', ''),
(11, 'Indenting - Plastic Raw Materials', 'Polypropylen.jpg', 'indenting-plastic-raw-materials', NULL, '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">Our rich vendor base helps us in offering qualitative series of <strong>Plastic Raw Materials</strong> Importer and agent in Bangladesh that\'s most suited for various applications. The Plastic Raw Material for instance pp, hd, gpps, abs, nylon and other plastics in virgin, prime, next to virgin, semi and reprocessed form. Client\'s can avail from everyone sorts of polymer, Resin like Polypropylene (PP) Injection, Polypropylene (PP) Film, Polypropylene (PP) Yarn, Polypropylene (PP) Copolymer, LLDPE ( Injection), HDPE Film, GPPS, HIPS, RESIN, ABS Resin, SAN Resin, PET Resin, Q Resin, PBT Resin, PU Resin, BOPP, LDPE Powder, PP Lamination, LDPE Lamination, EVA Etc. Our range is extensively designed for general purposes and engineering plastics. Moreover, our site delivers our range at industry leading prices.</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>For more details, please click on the links given below</strong></p>', ''),
(12, 'Textile Raw Materials And Chemicals', 'textile-Formic Acid.jpg', 'textile-raw-materials-Chemicals', NULL, '', '<p>We are engaged in offering a big selection of <strong>textile raw materials</strong> Importer and agent in Bangladesh. That\'s most suited for various applications. We handle all types of textile raw materials like Cationic Softener, Caustic Soda (Solid, Flakes, Pearls, Micropearls), Cotton Yarn, (Carded Yarn and Combed Yarn), Ferrous Sulphate, Formic Acid, Grey and Ecru Melange Yarn, Hydrogen peroxide, Polyester Yarn, Pretreatment, Dyeing and Finishing Auxillaries, Silicon Softener, Silicone Oil, Soda Ash Light, Sodium Meta -Bi- Sulphite, Sodium Sulphate Anhydrous (Glauber Salt), Spandex Yarn, Special Finish Chemicals, Tapioca Starch, Tencel Yarn, Viscose Staple Fiber, Viscose Yarn . Client\'s can avail from us all kinds Textile Yarn, Fiber and Chemicals. We offer our range at industry leading prices.</p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p><strong>For more details, please click on the links given below</strong></p>', ''),
(13, 'Machinery', 'Machinery.jpg', 'machinery', NULL, '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">We deliver our client a good quality series of <strong>Machinery</strong>, which you ll find are produced from high grade quality raw materials. These Machinery can easily be customized adhering to the our precious customers specifications. we offer wide range of Machinery which can include Multifunctional Computer Thermal-Cutting Bag-Making Machine,Edge Folding And Rolling Machine,Six-Color Flexography Printing Machine,High Speed &nbsp;Die Rotary, Double Rewind Film Blowing Machine,PP Film Blowing Machine,Computer Bag-Making Machine (Bottom Sealing),PP/PE Flat Yarn Making Machine,BOPP Cutting Machine,4 side sealing machine,PP/LDPE/LLDPE Blowing Machine,Lamination Machine,Poly Bottom Cutting Machine etc.These Machinery are widely known because of its durability and quality. Our Machinery can possibly be availed at industrial leading price.</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>For more details please click on the links given below</strong></p>', ''),
